OL,3,CMan's fight to save his home and
OL,4,C'Fiesta Land' from bulldozer
OL,6,FA man from Cheltenham says he has not
OL,7,Fslept for weeks due to plans to
OL,8,Fdemolish his home to make way for a
OL,9,Fdual carriageway and thousands of new
OL,10,Fproperties.
OL,12,FAndrew Smith has lived on the
OL,13,FTewkesbury Road in Uckington for 22
OL,14,Fyears with his home known locally as
OL,15,F'Fiesta Land' because he uses it to
OL,16,Frepair and sell Ford cars.
OL,18,FGloucestershire County Council wants
OL,19,Fto buy Mr Smith's land to make way for
OL,20,Fthe 4,000-home 'Elms Park' development
OL,21,Fnear junction 10 of the M5.
