OL,3,CMan's fight to save his home and
OL,4,C'Fiesta Land' from bulldozer
OL,6,F"I'm not against progress but they
OL,7,Fneed to make me a sensible offer," Mr
OL,8,FSmith said.
OL,10,FThe 63-year-old told ITV News the row
OL,11,Fmeans he has not slept properly for
OL,12,Fweeks.
OL,14,FHe said: "In the last month it's
OL,15,Factually put me to my knees I'll be
OL,16,Fquite open and honest. I'm under the
OL,17,Fdoctor - I can't sleep.
OL,19,F"Literally I haven't slept properly
OL,20,Ffor a good five weeks.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
