OL,3,CMan's fight to save his home and
OL,4,C'Fiesta Land' from bulldozer
OL,6,F"At one stage I was under the crisis
OL,7,Fteam, I was put under the crisis team
OL,8,Fby my local GP.
OL,10,F"I'm past that stage now. But this is
OL,11,Fnot going to be the end. If it means
OL,12,Fthe High Court, I'll go to the High
OL,13,FCourt."
OL,15,FMr Smith says he also wants to build
OL,16,Fan annexe for his 88-year-old mother
OL,17,Fmove in with him. He claims he was
OL,18,Ftold he would never get permission due
OL,19,Fto the upcoming redevelopment.
