OL,6,FHe said: "One of the last things my
OL,7,Ffather said to me was look after your
OL,8,Fmother.
OL,10,F"It breaks my heart and I've broken
OL,11,Fdown several times."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for Gloucestershire
OL,14,FCounty Council said: "We are currently
OL,15,Fnegotiating with landowners over the
OL,16,Fpurchase of their property where
OL,17,Frequired to facilitate delivery of the
OL,18,FM5 Junction 10 scheme.
