OL,6,F"In this case the land is required to
OL,7,Fenable the associated widening of the
OL,8,FA4019 Tewkesbury Road.
OL,10,F"(We have) presented an offer to the
OL,11,Fproperty owner that accounts for both
OL,12,Fthe valuation of the property in
OL,13,Faccordance with relevant standards and
OL,14,Fguidance and also considers relevant
OL,15,Fcompensation which acknowledges the
OL,16,Flandowner's situation.
OL,18,F"These negotiations are confidential,
OL,19,Fand we cannot comment further on these.
